{
  "text": "On the other hand, AI could be designed as a Teachable Agent (TA) capitalizing on learningby-teaching interactions where students learn by teaching the TA (e.g., assessing its knowledge by asking it questions or by getting it to solve problems) (Biswas et al., 2005; Chase et al., 2009).",
